{"tid":2429042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會員啫啫滑雞煲#239336隻屈毛撚 肯死出嚟同我道歉未","createTime":"2021-03-02T04:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:56:49.000Z","uid":350194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e669093998863daf0375bd3b557269c6bbc269","tid":2429042,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"有警嫂拍抖陰表示依家出街好撚驚俾人知道自己同仔女係狗乸,狗仔狗女<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427895</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n鑒於對家不嬲都成日作故仔博同情抹黑我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我當然例牌都係笑鳩佢哋啦 但就無故俾個賤種屈毛同藍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uO9rYpv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuO9rYpv.png&h=2c413497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾時笑鳩對家吹水作故仔變咗藍同毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係你隻狗撚咁撚聽話 好撚信任佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再之後唔知講乜鳩因為我唔信同埋得我一個笑鳩呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九唔搭八 最後我cap咗其他巴打都有笑鳩對家好撚假 係咪全部都係鬼嚟 之後條撚樣就嬲撚咗pin我係五毛話我積極留言同埋抹黑他人 <br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母你無啦啦屈鳩我 我唔撚追住你黎屌同埋指出有其他巴打一齊笑鳩佢哋 咁叫抹黑他人 你老母生咗你個賤種幾時死全家<br />\n<br />\n利申 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"ffb78637f5e93ee0139f6774729a1cc85c306d0e","tid":2429042,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"我地cctai 話你係就係 洗撚證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d80fb7c446a8ddd7278d729563c505cade61e44","tid":2429042,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffb78637f5e93ee0139f6774729a1cc85c306d0e","tid":2429042,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"我地cctai 話你係就係 洗撚證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"笑撚咗 今次擺明明屈 個賤種咁都可以咁唔知醜講出嚟"},{"pid":"3bbcb129b5ce364e4e2c8b276c296bfc5bff8059","tid":2429042,"uid":350